<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Welcome to JayLink SMS</title>
  <style>
    /* Reset styles */
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      color: #333;
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #ffffff;
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #eaeaea;
    }
    .logo {
      color: #0284c7;
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 30px 20px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #888;
      border-top: 1px solid #eaeaea;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      background-color: #0284c7;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .social {
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .social a {
      margin: 0 10px;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #0284c7;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <div class="logo">Jay<span style="color: #0369a1;">Link</span> SMS</div>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <h2>Welcome to JayLink SMS, {{firstName}}!</h2>
      <p>Thank you for joining JayLink SMS, your reliable platform for SMS and voice messaging.</p>
      <p>We're excited to have you onboard. With JayLink, you can:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Send SMS messages to multiple recipients</li>
        <li>Make voice calls with text-to-speech capabilities</li>
        <li>Manage contacts and create groups</li>
        <li>Schedule messages for future delivery</li>
        <li>Track analytics and delivery reports</li>
      </ul>
      <p>To get started, login to your account and explore our features:</p>
      <div style="text-align: center;">
        <a href="{{appUrl}}/dashboard" class="button">Go to Dashboard</a>
      </div>
      <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, our support team is always ready to help.</p>
      <p>Best regards,<br>The JayLink Team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; {{currentYear}} JayLink SMS. All rights reserved.</p>
      {{!-- <p>123 Messaging Street, Communication City</p> --}}
      <div class="social">
        <a href="#">Twitter</a> | <a href="#">Facebook</a> | <a href="#">LinkedIn</a>
      </div>
      <p>You received this email because you signed up for a JayLink SMS account.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>